---

<section class="route-preview" aria-label="전국 운송 네트워크">
  <div class="container route-preview__inner">

    <div class="route-preview__text" data-aos="fade-right">
      <span class="section-label">Nationwide Network</span>
      <h2 class="section-title section-title--light">전국 운송 네트워크</h2>
      <p class="route-preview__desc">
        수도권에서 영남·호남까지, 로한물류의 냉동·냉장 노선이 전국을 잇습니다.<br />
        안성·칠곡 거점을 중심으로 환적·분기하여 화물의 신선도를 지키며 배송합니다.
      </p>
      <ul class="route-preview__points">
        <li>안성(수도권) · 칠곡(영남 환적) 거점 운영</li>
        <li>냉동 · 냉장 · 상온 전 온도대 대응</li>
        <li>영남 · 호남 권역 직배송 노선 확보</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/services" class="btn btn--inverted route-preview__cta">노선 자세히 보기</a>
    </div>

    <div class="route-preview__map" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="150">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 257.2 388" role="img"
           aria-label="로한물류 전국 운송 네트워크 지도" class="route-map">
        <!-- 대한민국 외곽선 (흰색 계열) -->
        <path class="route-map__land" d={KOREA_PATH} />

        <!-- 노선 (문어발) -->
        <g class="route-map__lines">
          {routeLines.map((l) => (
            <line x1={l.x1} y1={l.y1} x2={l.x2} y2={l.y2} />
          ))}
        </g>

        <!-- 노드 + 레이블 -->
        {routeNodes.map((n) => (
          <g class={n.hub ? 'route-map__node is-hub' : 'route-map__node'}>
            {n.hub && <circle class="pulse" cx={n.x} cy={n.y} r="6" />}
            <circle class="dot" cx={n.x} cy={n.y} r={n.hub ? 5 : 3} />
            <text class="lbl" x={n.x} y={n.y - 8} text-anchor="middle">{n.label}</text>
          </g>
        ))}
      </svg>

      <ul class="route-map__legend" aria-hidden="true">
        <li class="is-hub"><span></span>거점 · 환적 허브</li>
        <li><span></span>배송 권역</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .route-preview {
    background: var(--color-bg-dark);
    padding-block: var(--section-py);
  }

  .route-preview__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .route-preview__text .section-title { text-align: left; }

  .route-preview__desc {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.62);
    line-height: 1.82;
    margin-block: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .route-preview__points {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .route-preview__points li {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.65rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
  }

  .route-preview__points li::before {
    content: ''; display: inline-block;
    width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-accent); flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .route-preview__map {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;
  }

  .route-map {
    width: 100%; max-width: 300px;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 10px 34px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4));
  }

  /* 대한민국 땅 - 흰색 계열 */
  .route-map__land {
    fill: #eef3f9;
    stroke: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
    stroke-width: 1;
    stroke-linejoin: round;
  }

  /* 노선 */
  .route-map__lines line {
    stroke: var(--color-accent, #2d6bb5);
    stroke-width: 1.6;
    stroke-opacity: 0.7;
    stroke-linecap: round;
    stroke-dasharray: 4 5;
    animation: route-flow 1.6s linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes route-flow {
    to { stroke-dashoffset: -18; }
  }

  /* 노드 */
  .route-map__node .dot {
    fill: #ffffff;
    stroke: #1b4f8a;
    stroke-width: 1.5;
  }
  .route-map__node.is-hub .dot {
    fill: var(--color-accent, #2d6bb5);
    stroke: #ffffff;
    stroke-width: 1.8;
  }
  .route-map__node .pulse {
    fill: var(--color-accent, #2d6bb5);
    opacity: 0.45;
    transform-box: fill-box;
    transform-origin: center;
    animation: route-pulse 2.4s ease-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes route-pulse {
    0%   { transform: scale(1);   opacity: 0.5; }
    70%  { transform: scale(2.6); opacity: 0; }
    100% { transform: scale(2.6); opacity: 0; }
  }

  .route-map__node .lbl {
    font-size: 8.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
    fill: #1e293b;
    paint-order: stroke;
    stroke: rgba(238, 243, 249, 0.9);
    stroke-width: 2.4px;
    stroke-linejoin: round;
  }
  .route-map__node.is-hub .lbl {
    font-weight: 800;
    fill: #0f2f55;
  }

  /* 범례 */
  .route-map__legend {
    display: flex; gap: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
  }
  .route-map__legend li { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem; }
  .route-map__legend li span {
    width: 9px; height: 9px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: #ffffff; border: 1.5px solid #1b4f8a;
  }
  .route-map__legend li.is-hub span {
    background: var(--color-accent, #2d6bb5); border-color: #fff;
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .route-map__lines line { animation: none; stroke-dasharray: none; }
    .route-map__node .pulse { animation: none; opacity: 0; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .route-preview__inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
    .route-preview__text .section-title,
    .route-preview__text { text-align: center; }
    .route-preview__points { align-items: center; }
    .route-preview__cta {
      width: 100%; max-width: 320px; margin-inline: auto;
      display: block; text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>